body:
In my last game i was having a discussion with an enemy zed after he ulted three straight times before it went on CD, reason being the first two died while he was untargetable. So basically he became immune three times in one fight, and being a Zed hes an obvious focus target, which made it basically impossible.

His argument was, &quot;i didnt finish the animation before they died so it should reset&quot;

My argument, &quot;part of the spells effects (immunity) did go off so that should automatically put it on CD it doesn&#039;t matter if the whole spells effect went off, why is my team getting the bad end of the stick when he is wasting his ult on low hp targets.&quot;

I&#039;m just curious what others opinions are about this. The way it is now he could possibly ult 5 times in one fight, thus becoming untargetable 5 times, and not even put his ult on CD.
